        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Help Americans Never Get Unwanted Phone calls Act of 2019 or the HANGUP Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits a debt collector from robocalling or texting without consent an individual for purposes of collecting&nbsp;a debt owed to or guaranteed by the federal government. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
